### 1. List all projects
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects

###

### 2. Get by ID (exists)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects/1

###

### 3. Get by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects/999

###

### 4. Get by invalid ID (bad request)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects/abc

###

### 5. Create valid project
POST http://localhost:8787/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Project",
  "description": "Created via test"
}

###

### 6. Create — missing name (422)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "No name"
}

###

### 7. Create — unknown field (422)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Valid name",
  "badField": "not allowed"
}

###

### 8. Patch name only (200)
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Project Name"
}

###

### 9. Patch description only (200)
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "New description"
}

###

### 10. Patch — empty body (422)
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### 11. Delete project (204)
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/projects/2

###

### 12. Delete again — not found (404)
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/projects/2

###

### 13. List after deletion (count = 1)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects